<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>rclone on 奇迹森林</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/rclone/</link><description>Recent content in rclone on 奇迹森林</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 21:48:07 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.leshans.eu.org/tags/rclone/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>vps使用rclone挂载Google Drive教程</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/vps%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8rclone%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BDgoogle-drive%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 21:48:07 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/vps%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8rclone%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BDgoogle-drive%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</guid><description>&lt;p>其实 &lt;code>rclone&lt;/code> 挂载 &lt;code>Google Drive&lt;/code> 网上的教程已经很多了，但是大多数的教程都有一点点过时，与现在的实际操作有一点出入，故整理了当前的挂载操作，以防忘记。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="一-安装并配置-rclone">一、 安装并配置 rclone&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;code>首先在 vps 上一键安装 rclone：&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">curl https://rclone.org/install.sh &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> sudo bash
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>接下来在本地电脑上下载命令行操作的 rclone：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>访问 &lt;a class="link" href="https://rclone.org/downloads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>rclone 下载地址&lt;/a>，选择您的操作系统下载相应的 zip 包并解压。一会需要用得着。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>软件准备好中，&lt;code>在 vps 上开始配置&lt;/code>，执行：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">rclone config
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;code>选择 n&lt;/code>，新建一个&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">No remotes found, make a new one?
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">n) New remote
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">s) Set configuration password
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">q) Quit config
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">n/s/q&amp;gt; n
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>输入新建的名称，随意写:比如 &lt;code>283pan&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Enter name for new remote.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">name&amp;gt;283pan
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>选择要挂载的网盘类型，&lt;code>选择18&lt;/code>，&lt;code>Google Drive&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>填写OAuth client ID，输入&lt;code>client_id&lt;/code>、&lt;code>client_secret&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>选择Rclone对Google Drive 谷歌云盘的操作权限，我这里选择1，完整的访问权限&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">15
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">16
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">17
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">18
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">19
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Option scope.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Scope that rclone should use when requesting access from drive.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Choose a number from below, or type in your own value.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Press Enter to leave empty.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 1 / Full access all files, excluding Application Data Folder.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> \ (drive)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 2 / Read-only access to file metadata and file contents.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> \ (drive.readonly)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> / Access to files created by rclone only.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 3 | These are visible in the drive website.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> | File authorization is revoked when the user deauthorizes the app.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> \ (drive.file)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> / Allows read and write access to the Application Data folder.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 4 | This is not visible in the drive website.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> \ (drive.appfolder)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> / Allows read-only access to file metadata but
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> 5 | does not allow any access to read or download file content.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> \ (drive.metadata.readonly)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">scope&amp;gt; 1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>回车默认&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">7
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Option service_account_file.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Service Account Credentials JSON file path.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Leave blank normally.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Needed only if you want use SA instead of interactive login.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Leading `~` will be expanded in the file name as will environment variables such as `${RCLONE_CONFIG_DIR}`.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Enter a value. Press Enter to leave empty.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">service_account_file&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>是否要编辑高级配置，我这里选择n&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Edit advanced config?
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">y) Yes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">n) No (default)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">y/n&amp;gt; n
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p> &lt;/p>
&lt;p>询问是不是自动配置，选择n&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="复制rclone-authorize-drive-your-token-code这一长串代码红色框起来的地方">复制&lt;code>rclone authorize &amp;quot;drive&amp;quot; &amp;quot;Your Token Code&amp;quot;&lt;/code>这一长串代码,&lt;code>红色框起来的地方&lt;/code>&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/e14e26cf7cd20061f721d90b5f606de6.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="二下载rclone-windows版">二、下载rclone windows版&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://rclone.org/downloads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>https://rclone.org/downloads/&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/0a3618be8579c7bb4517a897dabe8a10.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="下载在本地的-rclone-压缩包解压后你应该能看到一个-rcloneexe类似下图">下载在本地的 &lt;code>rclone&lt;/code> 压缩包解压后，你应该能看到一个 &lt;code>rclone.exe&lt;/code>，类似下图&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/c2ff2f533fff4be0a135dfe6cde0eee2.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>空白处右键&amp;ndash;&lt;code>在此处打开命令行窗口&lt;/code>，或者&lt;code>cmd&lt;/code>进入你的&lt;code>rclone目录&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>打开cmd,粘贴前面复制的代码回车（红色框起来的地方）&lt;/p>
&lt;p>（&lt;code>浏览器&lt;/code>自动打开进入到谷歌账号登录界面，并&lt;code>选择同意授权&lt;/code>。由于是新申请的 API，所以谷歌会提醒该应用未经验证。但是左下角有一行小灰字，&lt;code>点击选择继续就能授权&lt;/code>）&lt;/p>
&lt;p>授权成功浏览器会提示 &lt;code>success：&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/3fde03baf64fa2e8c9bdc91d3123645f.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>此时返回命令行，等待几秒就能看见授权的 code 了。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/c8e213c767691b9501779bfb24632785.webp"
loading="lazy"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>&lt;code>如果出现下面这种情况（waiting for code），请往下看第五点&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/75387d004d80bef3b490d4f7118add2a.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20230810012334426"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>复制授权，回到vps终端，粘贴到 rclone 中。红色框起来的地方&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/f0a347b2b05250aaba0bb824a925d413.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20230810014110112"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>接下来 rclone 会询问是否为团队盘：&lt;code>选择n&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Configure this as a Shared Drive (Team Drive)?
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">y) Yes
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">n) No (default)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果您要挂载的就是团队盘，那么选择 y，不是的话就选择 n&lt;/p>
&lt;p>此时配置就已经结束了，退出 clone，开始挂载。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="三-挂载-google-drive">三、 挂载 Google Drive&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>首先新建一个文件夹用于挂载：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mkdir /google
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>开始挂载：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>rclone mount 283pan: /google --allow-other --allow-non-empty --vfs-cache-mode writes &amp;amp;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>其中 &lt;code>283pan&lt;/code> 是 rclone 配置时输入的配置名称，&lt;code>/google&lt;/code> 是挂载目录&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>​ 挂载出错请往下看第四点&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>检查挂载：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">df -h
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/626fa1df5fe52993cd3bd8b4868d373a.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20230810011416520"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>卸载挂载：（/google 为挂载目录）&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">fusermount -u /google
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p> &lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="四挂载出错解决">四，挂载出错解决&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>可能会报错：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">Fatal error: mount not ready
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>一般是因为缺少依赖导致的，我们选择安装&lt;/p>
&lt;p>centos 系使用：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">yum install -y fuse fuse3 或者 yum install fuse3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>debian 系使用：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">apt-get install fuse3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>再次执行挂载命令，如果没有报错，就是挂载成功了。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="五解决rclone生成不了token-code的问题">五，解决Rclone生成不了token code的问题&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://r2.leshans.eu.org/2023/08/20c21f5c2bd1496164aecb572c258dd2.webp"
loading="lazy"
alt="image-20230810012334426"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p> &lt;/p>
&lt;p>这是因为开了&lt;code>科学上网&lt;/code>，但是cmd没走代理。我用的是小狐狸，端口是&lt;code>7890&lt;/code>，如果和我一样，那就复制了往里敲&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">http_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>socks5://127.0.0.1:7890
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">https_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>socks5://127.0.0.1:7890
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>配置完之后，我们再跑一次 &lt;code>rclone authorize&lt;/code>，code显示出来了&lt;/p>
&lt;p>取消sock5代理&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">http_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">set&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nv">https_proxy&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>rclone开机自动挂载</title><link>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/10/</link><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jul 2023 23:57:49 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.leshans.eu.org/p/10/</guid><description>&lt;br>
&lt;h1 id="假设">假设:&lt;/h1>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>你已经挂载好了onedrive&lt;/li>
&lt;li>不能使用systemctl的请先在root下安装&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>apt install systemd-sysv &amp;amp;&amp;amp; reboot&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>使用&lt;code>df -h&lt;/code>命令查看是否成功&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>假设 name: &lt;code>odrive&lt;/code> 挂载目录是 &lt;code>/onedrive&lt;/code> 运行以下命令:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">#注意修改为你的挂载名字(name),以及挂载目录,使用df -h命令查看&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nv">command&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34; mount odrive:/ /onedrive --copy-links --no-gzip-encoding --no-check-certificate --allow-other --allow-non-empty --umask 000&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>继续:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">#以下是一整条命令，一起复制到SSH客户端运行&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">13
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">14
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cat &amp;gt; /etc/systemd/system/rclone.service &lt;span class="s">&amp;lt;&amp;lt;EOF
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">[Unit]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">Description=Rclone
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">After=network-online.target
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">[Service]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">Type=simple
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">ExecStart=$(command -v rclone) ${command}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">Restart=on-abort
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">User=root
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">[Install]
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">WantedBy=default.target
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">EOF&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>现在就可以使用&lt;code>systemctl&lt;/code>来挂载OneDrive了&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="heading">&lt;/h4>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl &lt;span class="nb">enable&lt;/span> rclone &lt;span class="c1">#开机自启&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl start rclone #启动
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl restart rclone #重启
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl status rclone #状态
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>